{"tid":1624142,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"手足, 見到D渣刀既仆街, 唔使驚, 唔使掉野","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:47:54.000Z","uid":196536,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"eb429d8f5ee6b46602795aa196af9ce7d0a462f6","tid":1624142,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"逼佢埋角<br />\n一人一支長柄(夠硬既)<br />\n捅撚到佢仆街陷家鏟<br />\n刀邊夠你支野長<br />\n唔好立亂玩火 燒親自己友唔好<br />\n香港人反抗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申: 講緊打機</span></span>"},{"pid":"c622388526bf10b5d9d5532711a82910630ad7d6","tid":1624142,"uid":34293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"係後面既手足直接起飛腳啦"},{"pid":"fb25826389aa5e368e0b7a8056fb008bc9b01b3e","tid":1624142,"uid":7550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:06:08.000Z","msg":"人定飛刀同你一換一咁點"},{"pid":"122b4b36413fbb80720de446a2ded3e1662c1bc2","tid":1624142,"uid":194361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"以下係我朋友心聲<br />\n真的，我們甚麼都沒有，我甚麼都沒有<br />\n被政府迫害，被中共迫害，行街都會被狗咬<br />\n又唔打得<br />\n無車無樓無希望，好想自殺<br />\n我們手上甚麼也沒有，只剩一班勇武幫我地維護公義"},{"pid":"8b520bb49ccdfb095ca5ee7f8ef398cc4e1e1c73","tid":1624142,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:49.000Z","msg":"我知你講緊monster hunter"},{"pid":"0e24864ac517bb4ff6f1c144c1454f1e41dbc6d0","tid":1624142,"uid":11948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"同埋見到手足用長竹攻上身，下次描住下體就得，佢擋得下面上面就會失守"},{"pid":"b02d838de3dcbaa7282445997e26eb7ac67f8aef","tid":1624142,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"手足用唔用得刀 劈返佢"},{"pid":"5fddfdd152f97869f0a0e8ab5c53da90d251643a","tid":1624142,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9564a1f5bb7760f705a54ce610a3b48